FROM transactions_1k t 
JOIN yearmonth y ON t.CustomerID = y.CustomerID 
WHERE t.ProductID = 5 AND t.Price / t.Amount > 29.00 AND y.Date = '201208';	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
1:
SELECT date_received 
FROM income 
JOIN member ON income.link_to_member = member.member_id 
WHERE member.first_name = 'Connor' AND member.last_name = 'Hilton' AND source = 'Dues' 
ORDER BY date_received DESC 
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	student_club
2:
SELECT CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN T1.amount = 50 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(T1.member_id) 
FROM income AS T1 
JOIN member AS T2 ON T1.link_to_member = T2.member_id 
WHERE T2.t_shirt_size = 'Medium' AND T2.position = 'Member';	----- bird -----	student_club
3:
SELECT CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN p.SEX = 'F' AND strftime('%Y', p.Birthday) > '1930' THEN p.ID ELSE NULL END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(p.ID) AS Percentage 
FROM Patient p;	----- bird -----	thrombosis_prediction
4:
SELECT P.ID, P.SEX, P.Birthday 
FROM Patient P 
JOIN Laboratory L ON P.ID = L.ID 
WHERE L.LDH > 500;	----- bird -----	thrombosis_prediction
5:
SELECT P.ID, CAST((strftime('%Y', 'now') - strftime('%Y', P.Birthday)) AS REAL) AS age 
FROM Patient P 
JOIN Laboratory L ON P.ID = L.ID 
WHERE L.HCT >= 52 
GROUP BY P.ID 
HAVING COUNT(L.ID) >= 2;	----- bird -----	thrombosis_prediction

SELECT CAST(SUM(p.long_shots) AS REAL) / COUNT(pa.date) 
FROM Player p 
JOIN Player_Attributes pa ON p.player_api_id = pa.player_api_id 
WHERE p.player_name = 'Ahmed Samir Farag';	----- bird -----	european_football_2
7:
SELECT circuits.circuitRef 
FROM circuits 
WHERE circuits.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit';	----- bird -----	formula_1
8:
SELECT c.name, MIN(l.time) as lap_record 
FROM circuits c 
JOIN results r ON c.circuitId = r.raceId 
JOIN lapTimes l ON r.driverId = l.driverId AND r.raceId = l.raceId 
WHERE c.country = 'Italy' 
GROUP BY c.name 
ORDER BY lap_record ASC 
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	formula_1
9:
SELECT colour.colour AS EyeColor, COUNT(superhero.id) AS Count 
FROM superhero 
JOIN colour ON superhero.eye_colour_id = colour.id 
JOIN publisher ON superhero.publisher_id = publisher.id 
WHERE publisher.publisher_name = 'Marvel Comics' 
GROUP BY colour.colour 
ORDER BY Count DESC 
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	superhero
10:

FROM superhero AS T1

11:

FROM superhero

12:
SELECT gender.gender 
FROM superhero 
JOIN gender ON superhero.gender_id = gender.id 
WHERE hero_power.power_id IN ( 
    SELECT id FROM superpower WHERE power_name = 'Phoenix Force' 
)

HAVING COUNT(*) = ( 
    SELECT COUNT(*) 
    FROM superhero 
    JOIN superpower ON superhero.id = hero_power.hero_id 
    WHERE superpower.power_name = 'Phoenix Force' 
) 
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	superhero

15:
SELECT 
    CAST(SUM(v.UpVotes) AS REAL) / COUNT(u.Id) AS AverageUpVotes, 
    CAST(SUM(u.Age) AS REAL) / COUNT(u.Id) AS AverageAge 
FROM 
    users u 
JOIN 
    votes v ON u.Id = v.UserId 
WHERE u.Id IN ( 
    SELECT OwnerUserId FROM posts GROUP BY OwnerUserId HAVING COUNT(*) > 10 
);	----- bird -----	codebase_community

FROM atom

    ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC

);	----- bird -----	toxicology

       molecule.label
